        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of systemic arterial hypertension;

          -  Must be able to reality physical exercise.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes mellitus;

          -  Chronic renal failure;

          -  Body mass index ≥ 35kg/m2;

          -  Coronary artery disease;

          -  Heart failure;

          -  Use of beta-blocker;

          -  Uso of alpha-blocker;

          -  Smoker;

          -  Menopause (woman).
